OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHolocaust survivors        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcriticise plans for new    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fmemorial                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A 98-year-old Holocaust survivor has   
OL,6, told MPs that plans for a new memorial 
OL,7, and learning centre next to Parliament 
OL,8, are "completely idiotic".              
OL,10,FAnita Lasker-Wallfisch told a Commons  
OL,11,Fcommittee that the chosen location was 
OL,12,F"dangerous" and "impossible".          
OL,14,FMinisters first promised a memorial in 
OL,15,F2015, but the proposal proved          
OL,16,Fcontentious and has run into legal     
OL,17,Fdifficulties.                          
OL,19,FThe government said it remained "firmly
OL,20,Fcommitted" to the plan.                
